"title": "5204: age",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5204: age",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The number of years reached or expected to be reached in a human life. The span of life is determined by God and may be divided into distinct phases, each with its own characteristics. The term may also refer to an era of history, particularly in contrasting the present age with the coming age to be inaugurated at Jesus Christ's return.</p>\n<h2>The span of life</h2>\n<h3>In God's hands</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:27\">MAT 6:27</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:25\">LUK 12:25</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam2:6\">1SA 2:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps139:16\">PSA 139:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl8:8\">ECC 8:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas4:14-Jas4:15\">JAS 4:14–4:15</a></p>\n<h3>Longevity in the OT</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen5:5\">GEN 5:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen5:27\">GEN 5:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen9:29\">GEN 9:29</a>GEN <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen6:3\">6:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen25:7\">GEN 25:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen47:28\">GEN 47:28</a></p>\n<h3>The present-day span of life</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps90:10\">PSA 90:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam5:4-2Sam5:5\">2SA 5:4–5:5</a> <em>David lives to be 70</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam19:34-2Sam19:35\">2SA 19:34–19:35</a> <em>Barzillai, aged 80, expects to die soon</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa23:15\">ISA 23:15</a></p>\n<h3>Its apparent brevity</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps39:4-Ps39:6\">PSA 39:4–39:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen47:9\">GEN 47:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job7:6\">JOB 7:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps89:47\">PSA 89:47</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps90:3-Ps90:6\">PSA 90:3–90:6</a></p>\n<h3>Long life is a blessing from God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov10:27\">PRO 10:27</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps91:16\">PSA 91:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov3:1-Prov3:2\">PRO 3:1–3:2</a></p>\n<h2>Phases of human life</h2>\n<h3>Importance associated with age</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen43:33\">GEN 43:33</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam16:6-1Sam16:11\">1SA 16:6–16:11</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke22:26\">LUK 22:26</a></p>\n<h3>The age of discretion</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John9:21-John9:23\">JHN 9:21–9:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke2:42\">LUK 2:42</a></p>\n<h3>The age of maturity: 20 years</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev27:3\">LEV 27:3</a></strong> <em>Adulthood reckoned from the age of 20</em>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num26:2-Num26:4\">NUM 26:2–26:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num1:3\">NUM 1:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num1:45\">NUM 1:45</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num14:29\">NUM 14:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num32:11\">NUM 32:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh5:41\">JOS 5:41</a>CH <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh23:24\">23:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr31:17\">2CH 31:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra3:8\">EZR 3:8</a></p>\n<h3>Full maturity reckoned from the age of 30</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke3:23\">LUK 3:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num4:3\">NUM 4:3</a> <em>Levites assumed their duties at the age of 30</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num8:24\">NUM 8:24</a> <em>From the ages of 25 to 30, Levites may have served an apprenticeship.</em></p>\n<h3>Old age</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev27:7\">LEV 27:7</a></strong> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num4:47\">NUM 4:47</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num8:25-Num8:26\">NUM 8:25–8:26</a></p>\n<h2>Mountains as symbols of age</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab3:6\">HAB 3:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen49:26\">GEN 49:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job15:7\">JOB 15:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps90:2\">PSA 90:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov8:25\">PRO 8:25</a></p>\n<h2>Ages of history</h2>\n<h3>Before Jesus Christ was revealed</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph3:9\">EPH 3:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom16:25-Rom16:26\">ROM 16:25–16:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor10:11\">1CO 10:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:26\">COL 1:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb1:1-Heb1:2\">HEB 1:1–1:2</a></p>\n<h3>The present evil age</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal1:4\">GAL 1:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor1:20\">1CO 1:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor2:6-1Cor2:8\">1CO 2:6–2:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor4:4\">2CO 4:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:2\">EPH 2:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus2:12\">TIT 2:12</a></p>\n<h3>The end of this age</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:49\">MAT 13:49</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:39-Matt13:40\">MAT 13:39–13:40</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:3\">MAT 24:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:10\">MAT 24:10</a></p>\n<h3>The age to come</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt19:28-Matt19:29\">MAT 19:28–19:29</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:30\">MRK 10:30</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:30\">LUK 18:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke20:34-Luke20:36\">LUK 20:34–20:36</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:7\">EPH 2:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:19\">1TI 6:19</a></p>\n<h3>Blessing in the present age</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb6:5\">HEB 6:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt28:20\">MAT 28:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:15\">MRK 1:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:21\">EPH 1:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb9:26\">HEB 9:26</a></p>",
